```plantuml
@startuml SocialGouv_archifiltre-docs

actor User
participant "Desktop App" as App
participant "File System Loader" as FSLoader
participant "Hash Calculator" as HashCalc
participant "VFS" as VFS
participant "AsyncWorker" as AsyncWorker
participant "Exporter" as Exporter
participant "UI" as UI

User -> App: Open Application
App -> FSLoader: Load File System
FSLoader -> VFS: Create VFS Structure
FSLoader -> HashCalc: Calculate Hashes
HashCalc -> AsyncWorker: Offload Hash Calculation
AsyncWorker -> HashCalc: Return Hash Results
HashCalc -> VFS: Update VFS with Hashes
App -> UI: Display File System Data

User -> UI: Request Data Export
UI -> Exporter: Initiate Export Process
Exporter -> AsyncWorker: Offload Export Task
AsyncWorker -> Exporter: Return Export Results
Exporter -> UI: Display Export Completion

@enduml
```